downloadTitle: Dynamics 365 for Project Service Automation Sample Data V3
downloadDescription: The Project Service sample data package installs the "Fabrikam Manufacturing Master Data" (v3.0.0.0) solution with approximately ~4k records across 33 entities
detailsSection:
To become familiar with Dynamics 365 for Project Service Automation(PSA), it's useful to have a small, pre-configured dataset that makes it easy to trace through end to end scenarios.

For this purpose, we've created a seperate PSA only sample data installation package(English-language only at this time) that makes it easier to explore and learn about PSA.

Running this install performs the following:
1) Provide setup data which wil default the behaviour of PSA
2) Installs other sample data such as Bookable Resources, Roles, Sales and Cost Price Lists, Org Units and other reference data

IMPORTANT: Currently, there is no way to un-install this sample data. This package should only be used on demonstration, evaluation, training and test systems.
systemRequirementsSection: Microsoft Dynamics 365 (v9.0) with Project Service Automation(v3+)
installInstructionSection:
Please visit "https://aka.ms/fpsrefdata" for the latest and greatest instructions.
Download the self-extracting file, extract the contents to a working folder and update the necessary configuration files as specified in the instructions in the PkgFolder sub-folder.
